TITLE: Using FormatProviderAttribute for Culture-Specific String Formatting in Mapperly (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `FormatProviderAttribute` in Mapperly to specify a culture-specific format provider for string conversions. It shows how to define a default format provider and a specific format provider for a property using `MapPropertyAttribute`.
